data.description: Welcome to your new Baton Rouge home! This charming property sitting on a full 1 acre lot, offers recent updates throughout, promising comfort and convenience. Needs some repairs to the roof, siding, and some flooring, this house presents an excellent opportunity for buyers looking to add sweat equity in a sought-after area.   Enjoy the spacious interior filled with natural light and the modern kitchen perfect for culinary adventures and entertaining. The generous yard is ideal for outdoor activities and gatherings. Located in a desirable neighborhood with easy access to amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss out on this great price for a beautiful home. Closing set for mid-May. Property to be sold as-is. Schedule a showing today!
